# Release Process

## Version Update

Update:

```
src/report/run_metadata.py
```

Example:

```json
{
    "version":
        "0.2.0"
}
```

---

## Validation

Run:

```bash
pytest
```

Run sample analysis:

```bash
PYTHONPATH=src python3 -m app.main \
    --input sample_bundle.tgz \
    --output reports
```

Verify:

```
reports/

└── timestamp/

    ├── metadata.json

    ├── report.json

    └── summary.md
```

